snippet.title: Game & Watch - Lifeboat (c)1983 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description:
Emulation once again by algestam
As with Blackjack the artwork was provided by hydef and shows the full case.  hydef's artwork can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1IbSRYTfKoKDgZfJZTZdnKFSpBvCvgJZV
